/* mchoi John M Choi */

Usage for prob_3_1 is ./prob_3_1 filename
Prob_3_1 makes three threads, one for calculating the sum, one for calculating
the max, and one for calculating the min of the numbers in the input file.

Usage for prob_3_2 is ./prob_3_2 filename
Prob_3_2 makes three threads, each one working with 1/3 of the list of numbers
from the input file.

Both programs will output the results in the main thread and quit.
Race condition is handled in prob_3_2 with mutex locks.
To compile both programs, type in "make clean" and "make"
